(1,1,'Esther','Alabaster','img_uploaded/3464b64a922f7d911d69633167d3700d8c0b3049.jpg','A powerful narrative exploring themes of courage, faith, and resilience through the biblical story of Queen Esther, who risked everything to save her people from destruction.',1,'2025-12-27 16:41:19'),
