(6,6,'Milwaukee Mission','Elder Cooper Low','img_uploaded/a51e4e8d4f0a8f949ffc36f695d46fb1f5d7bf03.jpg','A compelling account of community service, urban challenges, and the transformative power of dedicated mission work in Milwaukee.',1,'2025-12-27 16:41:19'),
